Description: Denodo provides a data virtualization software that can integrate data from disperse stores (e.g. EDWs, Data Lakes, files, SaaS, enterprise apps., etc.) and deliver a unified data model that can be consumed from reporting tools and enterprise applications.

Name: Denologix, Inc.
Description: At Denologix we provide expert SAS services and support for all SAS technologies and the latest versions. Our competitive rates and fixed price services help you receive the most value possible from SAS. Denologix has been a premier SAS Partner for 15 years. In Collaboration with SAS Canada, Denologix has participated in the majority SAS Canada Implementations.
Additional Experience: Analytic Modernization, Customer Intelligence, Fraud (Security Intelligence), Risk Management

Name: Domino Data Lab (US)
Description: Domino Data Lab is an open, unified, enterprise-ready data science platform that allows organizations to build, validate, deliver, and monitor models at scale. This accelerates research, sparks collaboration, increases iteration speed, and removes deployment friction to deliver impactful models.
Industries: Public Sector/Government, Financial Services, Agriculture, Pharmaceutical, Energy and Utilities, Retail, Media and Entertainment, Manufacturing, Insurance, Telecommunications, Aerospace, Health Care and Life Sciences

Name: Dr. Nagler & Company GmbH
Description: Nagler & Company is a mid-sized consulting firm for financial industry that has experienced steady growth since its founding in the late 1990s. Our focus is on professional services for front office and market data systems, as well as risk management. Our services range from technical conception to operational realization; from analysis to transformation into processes; from choosing a system to embedding it into your IT landscape; from launch of financial applications through to maintenance. With Nagler & Company, you take advantage of interdisciplinary teams of IT specialists, mathematicians, physicists and economists. These diverse perspectives are key to your success.

Name: Dremio Corporation
Description: Dremio is the easy and open lakehouse platform. Data teams use Dremio to deliver self-service analytics, while enjoying the flexibility to use Dremio's lightning-fast SQL query service and any other processing engine on the same data. Dremio increases agility with a revolutionary data-as-code approach that enables Git-like data experimentation, version control, and governance. In addition, bringing together SAS and Dremio eliminates data silos by enabling queries across data lakes, databases, and data warehouses, and simplifying ingestion into the lakehouse.

Name: Dropsource
Description: Dropsource is a low-code mobile app development platform that allows organizations to leverage their enterprise data in building truly native enterprise-grade apps. With a powerful drag-and-drop UI, developers can easily develop, deploy, and maintain enterprise mobile apps without sacrificing quality or performance, and in a fraction of the time of yesterday's tools.
Industries: Telecommunications, Retail, Hospitality, Human Resources, Manufacturing, Insurance, Financial Services, Health Care and Life Sciences, Pharmaceutical, Aerospace, Media and Entertainment, Agriculture, Education

Name: Dunavnet
Description: DunavNET is an IoT solution design company, creating IoT turnkey solutions and helping our clients to digitally transform their businesses. DunavNET team is a mix of highly skilled system architects and software designers educated to MSc and PhD levels, specialising in development of IoT solutions using Microsoft Azure as the main platform. The technology expertise is complemented with domain expertise in agriculture, smart cities, and manufacturing enabling us to not only visualize raw data, but also to analyse data and provide actionable knowledge.
